Package com.filestack

Filestack is an easy API for file uploading, conversion, and delivery.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileLink
    References and performs operations on an individual file.
    FilestackClient
    Uploads new files.
    Policy
    Determines what access a user is allowed (if account security is enabled).
    Policy.Builder
    Builds new Policy.
    Security
    Holds a Policy and its signature.
    UploadOptions
    Configures storage options for a new upload.
    UploadOptions.Builder
    Builds new UploadOptions.
